            "title": "盤中速報 - 順德(2351)大漲7.43%，報107元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>順德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2351-TW</a>)07日11:46股價上漲7.4元，報107.0元，漲幅7.43%，成交4,609張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>順德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2351-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為半導體導線架。五金文具用品。模具及其他。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.57%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.17%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+560 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+670 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-110 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,171 張</li> <li>融券增減：+476 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
